HEADWORD: extrovertive
<hw>extrovertive</hw></mhw> <pos>adj.</pos>
<sn>1.</sn> <fld>(Psychol.)</fld> <def>directed outward; marked by an
interest in other people or concerned primarily with external
reality.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> extrovert, extravert, extraverted, extravertive,
